26 Imgur Creator Spotlight: Something a little different tonight! A podcast! @Ilovedowlsandcatsbeforeallofyouguyspickeduponthis and her husband, who has made documentaries for National Geographic and BBC) have a podcast called No Ordinary Monday. It features people with different types of jobs and the main story is about the guest's most unique/impactful moment or experience during their career. They're like interesting little mini-documentaries. I've listened and I think they're fascinating. Give them a try! Podcast (audio) - https://pods.link/noordinarymonday Podcast (video) - https://www.youtube.com/@noordinarymonday They're always looking for listener stories, potential guests, and community engagement. People can reach out on the website or on socials https://linktr.ee/Noordinarymonday (I know it's a lot of links, not an ad, not trying to get you to buy something, featuring a fellow imgurian's work, like always! Be supportive)
